{
  "text": "This animal protocol was in accordance with the German guidelines for use of living animals and was approved by the Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee of the T\u00fc bingen University Hospital and the Regierungspr\u00e4 sidium T\u00fc bingen or the University of Colorado guidelines for animal care. To define the contribution of renal or hematopoietic A2BARs during renal ischemia or IP, we generated bone marrow chimeric mice in which bone marrow was ablated by radiation in WT mice (C57BL/6) followed by reconstitution with bone marrow derived from previously characterized mice gene-targeted for the A2BAR [CITATION_1] and vice versa (A2BAR",
